e","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Allows to select the balance between result accuracy (precision) and missed barcodes (recall) for linear barcodes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Some barcode types are naturally prone to false positives (e.g. MSI Plessey)."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"For those barcode types false positives can be drastically reduced (precision can be increased) by requiring that multiple scan-lines in the input scan to the same result.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, this stronger condition can lead to missed barcodes (lower recall).","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Confirmation is avoided for barcode types, which are by design resistant to false positives, (e.g. Code128) to maximize recall.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode/thorough":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Recommended. Thorough confirmation is performed. Almost completely eliminates false positives, at the cost of an additional slight decrease in recall.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode\/thorough","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkonedconfirmationmode\/thorough","title":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode.thorough","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationModeThorough"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"thorough"}]},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK":{"title":"ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK","type":"t